title: #712 - Eliza James
description:
Eliza James, a professional violinist who has toured the world and performed with stars such as Kanye West and Taylor Hicks, joins Joey Diaz and Lee Syatt LIVE in studio. For the past 16+ years Eliza has been the featured solo violinist in Burt Bacharach's touring band and has held the same position in Paul Anka’s touring band for more than 6 years.
